01:45:03,300 --> 01:45:04,600
Wait.

2153
01:45:04,700 --> 01:45:06,500
Oh, shit!

2154
01:45:06,700 --> 01:45:09,000
Oh, my God...

2155
01:45:09,100 --> 01:45:12,000
Mark pretty much cleaned them
