2182
01:46:25,200 --> 01:46:27,100
and touched every American.

2183
01:46:27,200 --> 01:46:29,500
We're sorry for the...

2184
01:46:29,700 --> 01:46:31,700
disadvantage to this young man.

2185
01:46:31,900 --> 01:46:34,600
K-Mart is phasing out the sale
of handgun ammunition.

2186
01:46:34,700 --> 01:46:38,300
The business plan calls
for this to be complete

2187
01:46:38,400 --> 01:46:42,000
in the continental U.S.
within the next 90 days.

2188
01:46:42,200 --> 01:46:43,500
Wow! Wow!

2189
01:46:43,700 --> 01:46:45,500
K-Mart representatives met
with Mr. Moore

2190
01:46:45,600 --> 01:46:47,900
and the students from Columbine,
