for them within a week's time.

2195
01:47:00,100 --> 01:47:03,100
Well, the first thing we want
to do is thank you

2196
01:47:03,400 --> 01:47:06,500
for committing to no longer
selling handgun ammunition

2197
01:47:06,600 --> 01:47:08,400
in your stores.
