2198
01:47:08,700 --> 01:47:11,000
The process will be phased out
within 90 days.

2199
01:47:11,200 --> 01:47:13,500
And after 90 days,
there will be no more selling

2200
01:47:13,700 --> 01:47:16,500
of ammunition that can go into
handguns or assault weapons.

2201
01:47:16,600 --> 01:47:18,800
Firearm ammunition, will be...
We will not sell it,

2202
01:47:18,900 --> 01:47:20,800
after 90 days, in our stores.

2203
01:47:21,000 --> 01:47:23,700
- We greatly appreciate that.
- Thank you.

2204
01:47:23,800 --> 01:47:25,900
Thank you very much. Thank you.
That's very brave.

2205
01:47:29,000 --> 01:47:30,700
Thank you. Wow!

2206
01:47:30,800 --> 01:47:34,000
That blows my mind. That's
more than what we asked for.

2207
01:47:34,300 --> 01:47:37,000
- It's remarkable.
- Yeah. Well, like I told you--

2208
01:47:37,100 --> 01:47:39,000
- I didn't think--
