2211
01:47:44,600 --> 01:47:47,900
The kids from Columbine had
scored an overwhelming victory

2212
01:47:48,100 --> 01:47:49,900
against K-Mart
and it inspired me

2213
01:47:50,000 --> 01:47:54,100
to do something that
