2214
01:47:54,400 --> 01:47:56,900
All I needed... was a star map.

2215
01:48:17,700 --> 01:48:19,400
- Hello?
- Mr. Heston?

2216
01:48:19,500 --> 01:48:21,400
- Yeah.
- This is Michael Moore.

2217
01:48:21,500 --> 01:48:22,900
- Yes.
- The film- maker?

2218
01:48:23,100 --> 01:48:25,000
- Yes, of course.
- Yes. How you doing?

2219
01:48:25,100 --> 01:48:26,500
Fine, thank you.

2220
01:48:26,500 --> 01:48:29,700
Listen, I was wondering
if maybe I could talk to you.

2221
01:48:30,000 --> 01:48:33,300
We're making a documentary
about the whole gun issue.

2222
01:48:33,400 --> 01:48:35,200
And I'm a member of the NRA.

2223
01:48:35,500 --> 01:48:38,000
I thought maybe we could talk
a little bit about--

2224
01:48:38,100 --> 01:48:39,800
Tell you what, let me look
at my calendar.

2225
01:48:40,100 --> 01:48:42,500
I may be able to give you
some time tomorrow.

2226
01:48:42,600 --> 01:48:45,500
- I have some people here now.
